pharmacy /ˈfɑːməsɪ/

(pharmacies) 

1. N-COUNT A pharmacy is a shop or a department in a shop where medicines are sold or given out. 药店; 药房 

例： Pick up the medicine from the pharmacy. 从药房取药。 

2. N-UNCOUNT Pharmacy is the job or the science of preparing medicines. 制药业; 药剂学 

例： He spent four years studying pharmacy. 他花了4年时间学习药剂学。

